text: Nikolayevka () is a rural locality (a village) in Miyakibashevsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 13 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 22 km from Anyasevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Nikolayevka, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
